_comment: This data is an early work-in-progress and contains errors. Produced by @michaelh at Discuss and Discover SuttaCentral forum - please get in touch! Finished code forthcoming.

How diversity of elements gives rise to: The eye element gives rise to eye contact
Eye contact doesn’t give rise to the eye element
The ear element gives rise to ear contact
Ear contact doesn’t give rise to the ear element
The nose element gives rise to nose contact
Nose contact doesn’t give rise to the nose element
The tongue element gives rise to tongue contact
Tongue contact doesn’t give rise to the tongue element
The body element gives rise to body contact
Body contact doesn’t give rise to the body element
The mind element gives rise to mind contact
Mind contact doesn’t give rise to the mind element
